## Board Game Night Rules Sheet

**Host:** {person}

**Setup:** Clear the {place}, deploy {number} {adjective} chairs, shuffle the {plural noun} deck twice.

**House rules:**
- No {verb ending in -ing} during someone else's turn
- Snacks must be {adjective} and not {color}
- Disputes settled by {person} or a {object} coin flip

**Turn order:** Youngest player {verb ending in -ing} first, then clockwise by {emotion}

**Penalties:** Lose one {food} token if you {verb} the board

**Victory dance:** Winner must {verb} while holding a {clothing item}

**Cleanup:** Everyone helps {verb} {plural noun} back into the box.
